long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ICBCAssistChromeExtension is an extension program designed to assist the ICBC Internet Banking Assistant application. It will help ICBC online banking open the online banking assistant, determine whether to install the online banking assistant application and other related operations. ICBCAssistChromeExtension helps ICBC client better use the online banking system.
